{"tid":334786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北上注意】廣州民眾用充電站 幾分鐘被裝好多app","createTime":"2017-07-25T05:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T05:09:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d32d28f55cb9627623bcb50c8a9bfc3fe9f7b698","tid":334786,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500882005_e4b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500882005_e4b2.jpg&h=75395dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經常北上的市民要注意，不要隨便充電！廣州有民眾稱把電話放在市面上的充電站時，幾分鐘便被裝上四、五個app，五花八門、來路不明，專家稱若這些app是惡意程式，不法份子隨時可遙距盜取機主的個人信息。<br />\n<br />\n姓史的廣州民眾，曾經有這樣無故被裝app的經歷。他說有一次在當地一間醫院內的充電站，在掃QR Code付款後，按要求點了一些設定後，幾分後便出現好幾個新的app，那些app甚麼類型都有，貸款軟件、線上金融、視頻軟件、瀏覽器，史見狀即時將充電線拔掉，刪掉軟件。史稱：「幸好只是安裝了一些軟件，沒有發生惡意扣費的情況。」<br />\n在中國其他大城市，曾有報道指民眾用充電站後，竟發現自己的私人照片、文件竟被非法盜取，甚至利用充電中的電話發送短信，在支付軟件內盜用資金，連銀行卡也可能被別人盜刷。<br />\n內地的安全專家王冬稱，部份充電站會誘使用戶打開「USB調試」（USB Debugging）的選項，這相當於將電話內部的權限交給充電站，充電站亦可意安裝app，甚至提取資料。王冬提醒民眾在使用充電站，或接上公共電腦時，應不要打開「USB調試」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170724/56996290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170724%2F56996290&d=CtS3Nn%2BaoEd%2BECsNizbbEpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8aa646b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170724%2F56996290&h=e604cefc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170724/56996290</a>"},{"pid":"54d350f4de0863cff325847fb69432f1635459b8","tid":334786,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"ANDROID 真係笑撚死人"},{"pid":"04d1ffb5d26e37ebc2ecd5776e90bf03c908de4d","tid":334786,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"705b86e6c785140ce06cf3191bf198856034d887","tid":334786,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"只有騙子才是真的"},{"pid":"04ec2395bf17a447a44632be120a1191a2b8b177","tid":334786,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ANDROID 真係笑撚死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}